messages.text: Why is he not letting you out?
You HAVE to leave that place
The door and windows are locked
In the basement. Building a hiding place in case the police come looking for him
Why would the police come look for him?
Break a window and get out
You said he's in the basement!
No I can't do this to him
Emily what he's doing to you isn't right
Please text me as soon as you can
I just want you to know Thelma he's a good man
Don't waste time collecting our stuff. I'll give you some clothes
Can you come pick me up?
Two houses down from your place
Watching TV with Matt. Can't leave the room
You have to distract him. Knock on the door and try to sell him something
I told him I was a Mormon and wanted to talk about my church
In the living room. He's making tea in the kitchen
Shit the front door is locked!
Cos you're a sneaky bitch and you can't wait to tell on us
What did you do to her?
I want to keep us all safe
LOL what do you think you're doing?
I won't let the police anywhere near me and my girlfriend
If you call them it's over.
Come down to the basement. We're having tea with Emily
No. I'm in the basement. With Emily. Our safe place.
Not at all. She's here because she wants to.
I couldn't have kept her here if she didn't want to.
I don't know what to say.
Will you talk to me for a few minutes?
I work with my mom at her hospital
Yes. It's the job I was meant to do.
Is there someone in your life?
I try not to hold on to anger.
You probably wouldn't be where you are if it weren't for me.
I'm it angry. I deserve every bit of it.
But I want to know... why did you escape? Why then?
You hurt someone else very badly.
I did it to protect us. I couldn't let her talk.
I panicked. She wouldn't stop screaming. I was drunk.
I don't want to hear about it anymore. I just want to forget.
Please don't hang up. Talk to me a little more.
Not really.. I was scared when I woke up and you weren't there. You had told me you would never leave me.
I understood you weren't who I thought you were.
Do you think I'm a bad man?
You see, I don't believe you. Because you agreed to talk to me, despite everything.
You're still able to see the good in me. Thank you. My last wish has been granted.
This was my last phone call, Emily. They're coming to take me away.
